{"tid":687884,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"支那式父母","createTime":"2018-06-02T16:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T18:02:09.000Z","uid":154054,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c273097693c13f286fd559b55857d141ec61063","tid":687884,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:00:30.000Z","msg":"自己一d個人興趣生活都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將仔女既人生當係玩緊rpg game 黎控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望子成龍又要每日圍住d仔女轉，乜都要聽晒佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係叻既人又點可能一d自己既想法都冇要聽d廢老鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一有d咩唔岩聽就搬「我咁為你好，我咁愛你，你竟然點點點」出黎，玩道德綁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不孝都要講，收皮啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d25ba6bd49d49df004c2afeedcc7481867bc20","tid":687884,"uid":128109,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:55:38.000Z","msg":"呢D叫情緒勒索。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542e6ce22cadff760151202ab1405cb42d86e6b6","tid":687884,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8d25ba6bd49d49df004c2afeedcc7481867bc20","tid":687884,"uid":128109,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:55:38.000Z","msg":"呢D叫情緒勒索。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"唔係，佢意思係話你好不孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65f2ea6ef009c1df7f81fcd5d9cb1032d063d0f","tid":687884,"uid":128109,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:08:40.000Z","msg":"Read this. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n//「我是為你好」這句話，表面上是以他人為出發點的關愛，但其實是一種情緒勒索，為的是達到自己的目的。 如果沒有照著他人的意思去做，就是壞人、就是背叛他人的好意。這樣的言語霸凌往往對接收者造成很大的心理壓力和負擔，甚至開始懷疑、認為自己真的就是這麼糟糕。 受到情緒勒索的人，一方面不想按照他人的意思去做，一方面又不想成為「壞人」。當長期在兩種情緒的拉扯、因為怎麼做都不對的煎熬下，人就會漸漸地失去自信。//<br />\n<br />\nFurther reading:<br />\n《「都是為你好」？別再以愛為名「情緒勒索」》<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/27/n9571620.htm/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F8%2F27%2Fn9571620.htm%2Famp&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7868b2d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/27/n9571620.htm/amp</a>"},{"pid":"bd41fcd5afaf79e3bf17d4d4a6dbdcbaab7e037d","tid":687884,"uid":184900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:10:01.000Z","msg":"亞洲式父母 + 亞州式教育"},{"pid":"fb303c7ec4f47d30a3734cce2807dd57c021ceba","tid":687884,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f65f2ea6ef009c1df7f81fcd5d9cb1032d063d0f","tid":687884,"uid":128109,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:08:40.000Z","msg":"Read this. <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n//「我是為你好」這句話，表面上是以他人為出發點的關愛，但其實是一種情緒勒索，為的是達到自己的目的。 如果沒有照著他人的意思去做，就是壞人、就是背叛他人的好意。這樣的言語霸凌往往對接收者造成很大的心理壓力和負擔，甚至開始懷疑、認為自己真的就是這麼糟糕。 受到情緒勒索的人，一方面不想按照他人的意思去做，一方面又不想成為「壞人」。當長期在兩種情緒的拉扯、因為怎麼做都不對的煎熬下，人就會漸漸地失去自信。//<br />\n<br />\nFurther reading:<br />\n《「都是為你好」？別再以愛為名「情緒勒索」》<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/8/27/n9571620.htm/amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F8%2F27%2Fn9571620.htm%2Famp&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAghME