\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T18:02:09.000Z","msg":"//知道咩回事自然有應對方法係d未試過既人先講得出口// 比粒膠你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你起馬自己諗到消極嘅應對方法呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thoughtsonlifeandlove.com/how-to-deal-with-emotional-blackmail/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thoughtsonlifeandlove.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-emotional-blackmail%2F&d=sMYxUHRkZZkXU%2BYeR80TAghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=619f284e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thoughtsonlifeandlove.com/how-to-deal-with-emotional-blackmail/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢篇文算係歸納左之前小弟嘅應對方法，身為情緒勒索者當然知自己弱點係邊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實講到尾，以小弟經驗，受害人都係要身邊嘅人去支持，比人扶一把，先至有信心跳躍去做返自己同埋有力去抵抗呢種陰濕嘅懷柔手段。唔好孤軍作戰啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}